ecoming-anti-china-bloc-minister-says-2024-07-11/</link><description>匈牙利外交部长彼得·西雅尔托周四表示，匈牙利不希望北约成为“反华”集团，也不会支持其这样做。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 13:07:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/hungary-will-not-support-nato-becoming-anti-china-bloc-minister-says-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>埃尔多安称拜登和美国涉嫌以色列战争罪的同谋</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/erdogan-says-biden-us-complicit-alleged-israeli-war-crimes-2024-07-11/</link><description>土耳其总统塔伊普·埃尔多安表示，美国总统乔·拜登及其政府在他所谓的以色列战争罪行和加沙冲突中违反国际法的行为中同谋，他呼吁对以色列实施制裁。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 12:44:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/erdogan-says-biden-us-complicit-alleged-israeli-war-crimes-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国红旗今年将在欧洲推出两款电动汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-hongqi-launch-two-electric-cars-europe-this-year-2024-07-11/</link><description>中国汽车制造商红旗将于今年晚些时候在欧洲推出电动 EH7 和 EHS7 车型，这是一个新的迹象，表明尽管最近宣布了欧盟关税，但中国汽车行业仍致力于欧洲扩张。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 11:45:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-hongqi-launch-two-electric-cars-europe-this-year-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>德国将从其5G核心网络中逐步淘汰华为、中兴组件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/germany-agrees-phaseout-huawei-zte-components-5g-core-network-2024-07-11/</link><description>德国内政部长周四表示，德国已与电信提供商达成协议，从 2029 年起将华为 (HWT.UL) 或中兴通讯等中国公司排除在该国 5G 网络产品之外。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 11:44:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/germany-agrees-phaseout-huawei-zte-components-5g-core-network-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>前领导人告诉G20，对超级富豪征税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/tax-super-rich-ex-leaders-tell-g20-2024-07-11/</link><description>前总统和总理向世界20大经济体现任领导人发出公开信，敦促支持对亿万富翁征收全球税，他们称这是一个难得的政治机会。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 11:20:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/tax-super-rich-ex-leaders-tell-g20-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：CPI 谨慎似乎没有障碍，英镑飙升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-11/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 10:03:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>由于红海延误，折扣商 Pepco 提前订购圣诞节发货</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/discounter-pepco-ordering-earlier-christmas-shipments-amid-red-sea-delays-2024-07-11/</link><description>欧洲折扣零售商 Pepco 集团老板周四表示，正从中国提前订购圣诞节货物，以确保在关键的节日交易期间及时交货。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 09:53:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/discounter-pepco-ordering-earlier-christmas-shipments-amid-red-sea-delays-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>大众旗下 MAN 和 E.ON 联手为电动卡车充电</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/vws-man-eon-cooperate-electric-truck-charging-2024-07-11/</link><description>德国能源公司 E.ON 和大众汽车子公司 MAN Truck &amp;amp; Bus 周四表示，计划从今年开始建立泛欧洲卡车充电网络。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 09:10:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/vws-man-eon-cooperate-electric-truck-charging-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，随着美国降息押注的巩固，亚洲外汇空头有所缓解</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/asian-fx-bears-ease-us-rate-cut-bets-solidify-2024-07-11/</link><description>路透周四的一项调查显示，由于对美联储今年至少降息两次的预期不断上升以及美元走软提振了风险情绪，大多数亚洲货币的空头头寸有所缓解。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 07:38:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/asian-fx-bears-ease-us-rate-cut-bets-solidify-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国全会交付的政策议程因目标相互冲突而受阻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-plenum-deliver-policy-agenda-hindered-by-conflicting-goals-2024-07-11/</link><description>中国领导人将在下周举行的备受期待的会议上寻求为经济注入信心，但相互冲突的目标，例如在削减债务的同时促进增长，可能意味着在实施变革方面进展甚微。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 07:15:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-plenum-deliver-policy-agenda-hindered-by-conflicting-goals-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>央行为何推出新的现金管理工具？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/why-does-chinas-central-bank-have-new-cash-management-tool-2024-07-11/</link><description>中国央行本周推出了一种新的现金管理工具，即临时债券回购协议和逆回购，增加了各种公开市场操作，并创造了可能成为重要利率指标的工具。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 06:04:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/why-does-chinas-central-bank-have-new-cash-management-tool-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国官方媒体称多个澳门政府网站遭到黑客攻击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/several-macau-government-websites-hacked-says-chinese-state-media-2024-07-11/</link><description>据中国官方媒体周三晚间报道，澳门多个政府网站遭到黑客攻击，警方已展开刑事调查，追查犯罪根源。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 00:14:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/several-macau-government-websites-hacked-says-chinese-state-media-2024-07-11/</guid></item></channel></rss>